data.title: Motorways in the United Kingdom

M10 Announcement

Bypasses the Medway Tow 41.4 18:47, 16 Dec 2005 (GMT) Medway M20 linking London (Swanley) and Folkestone. 81.4 19:01, 16 Dec 2005 (GMT) M23 linking London (Coulsdon) to beyond Crawley. 25.6 19:47, 16 Dec 2005 (GMT) All done except 2 junctions at Southern end. Need some tracks for these. M25 the London orbital motorway. 188.0 09:56, 16 Jun 2006 (UTC) Finished improving junctions based on yahoo imagery. M4, M1 still need work. --TimSC 16:55, 9 January 2008 (UTC) M26 a short link between the M25 at Sevenoaks and the M20 before Maidstone. 15.9 19:04, 16 Dec 2005 (GMT) M27 the south coast route running from Cadnam, west of Southampton, to Portsmouth. 40.0 23 March 2010 (UTC) M271 the Totton, Southampton spur from the M27 5.0 00:32, 3 April 2007 (BST) Both the north and south section are complete along with the one junction. M275 the Portsmouth spur from the M27 3.0 03:28, 17 Dec 2005 (GMT) Needs a southbound trace for the only junction. M3 linking Southampton and London 94.3 22 March 2011 M32 a spur from the M4 to central Bristol. 7.0 09:07, 02 Jan 2006 (GMT) Junctions need more GPS points M4 From London to South Wales 305.0 Tellytart 11:25, 4 November 2011 (UTC) Checked end to end first time - most junctions, bridges and tunnels now have correct layering. Junctions 1-5 Now double-checked and believed to be complete. M40 linking London with Birmingham at the M42 Birmingham orbital motorway . 144.0 16:51, 14 Jun 2006 (UTC) Someone has made some nice junctions between M25 and Oxford. Junctions from Oxford to M42 needed. Carriageways made into ways and labelled. M42 The southern and eastern part of the Birmingham orbital motorway extending north towards Ashby-de-la-Zouch and west to the M5. 88.0 19:48, 16 Dec 2005 (GMT) A few junctions have been completed towards the Eastern end between th M40 and M6. Junctions have now been correctly tagged at the diverging nodes, including numbered exits on the A42 towards the M1. M45 a short spur from the M1 north of Daventry towards Coventry. 12.5 19:23, 19 Dec 2005 (GMT) Complete M48 the Severn Bridge, linking Thornbury and Newport, Monmouthshire over the River Severn. This used to be the M4 before the Second Severn Crossing was built. 19.0 08:50, 07 Jan 2006 (GMT) M49 a short link from the M5 to the M4 west of Bristol. 8.0 20:22, 19 Dec 2005 (GMT) M5 linking Exeter and the south-west of England with Birmingham and the Midlands. 262.2 10:42, 31 Dec 2005 (GMT) Junctions have now been correctly tagged at the diverging nodes. M50 linking the M5 at Tewkesbury to Ross-on-Wye. 34.0 09:06, 02 Jan 2006 (GMT) Junctions have now been correctly tagged at the diverging nodes. M53 linking Chester and Birkenhead. 32.0 00:11, 20 Dec 2005 (GMT) M54 linking the M6 north of Wolverhampton and Telford. 40.0 EdLoach 09:12, 2 October 2008 (UTC) At least one access sliproad missing (eg M54 J1 westbound) M55 linking Blackpool and the M6 at Preston. 18.4 12:43, 21 Dec 2005 (GMT) M56 linking Manchester and Chester. 56.0 23:09, 07 Nov 2006 (GMT) Still missing the west/southbound carriageway between J2 and J3, carriageways split apart here. M57 a Liverpool bypass running north-west from the M62. 16.0 13:49, 22 Dec 2005 (GMT) M58 linking Wigan and northern Liverpool. 19.0 23:46, 22 Dec 2005 (GMT) M6 the western north-south motorway linking the M1 at Rugby with Carlisle. The section around Preston was the first stretch of motorway built. 364.8 23:50, 18 Dec 2005 (GMT) See United Kingdom motorways/M6 for full status. M6 Toll Toll Road 40.0 14:21, 18 Dec 2005 (GMT) Most juntions need to be added. M60 the Manchester Outer Ring Road, an orbital motorway. 56.0 23:10, 07 Nov 2006 (GMT) Missing some gps tracks for J6 to J8 with the newly opened 4 parallel carriageways. Junctions J6 to J13 need work. Junctions J21 to J27 need work. M602 M62 spur into Manchester. 7.0 13:16, 22 Dec 2005 (GMT) M606 M62 spur at Bradford. 5.0 11:18, 26 Dec 2005 (GMT) M61 linking Preston and Manchester. 32.0 22:24, 21 Dec 2005 (GMT) Need to add Bolton Services, J8 and J9 slip to Walton Summit rbt. M62 linking Liverpool and the approaches to Kingston-upon-Hull, the trans-Pennine link. 168.0 19:49, 16 Dec 2005 (GMT) Carriageways complete, just need some junctions now. East of Manchester needs Birch Services adding and work on all junctions from J18 east bound. M621 M62 spur at Leeds. 13.0 08:55, 07 Jan 2006 (GMT) M65 linking Preston and Colne, Lancashire. 48.0 18:20, 21 Dec 2005 (GMT) M66 linking Rawtenstall and the M62 at Manchester. 13.0 21:22, 22 Dec 2005 (GMT) M67 linking the M60 at Denton to Hyde in Greater Manchester. 8.0 23:01, 22 Dec 2005 (GMT) Clockwise logged with all junctions at 1 sec. M69 linking Leicester and Coventry. 24.0 13:12, 22 Dec 2005 (GMT) segments aligned, and ways tagged, some junctions need completing. M898 the Erskine Bridge approach road. 2.0 15:28, 18 Jun 2009 (BST) M9 linking Edinburgh and Stirling. 53.1 09:00, 30 Dec 2005 (GMT) M90 linking the Forth Road Bridge and Perth, Scotland. 48.0 18:01, 04 Jan 2006 (GMT) M96 not open to the public, but part of the Fire Service College at Moreton-in-Marsh. 1.0 10:09, 07 Jan 2006 (GMT) Not a motorway, properly re-tagged as highway=service.
